Satans Satyrs - Die Screaming 2014 320ak

Satan's Satyrs are the brainchild of vocalist/multi-instrumentalist Clayton "Claythanas" Burgess, formed in 2009 in Herndon, Virginia, USA while Clayton was still in high school. Burgess was influenced by both punk rock and doom metal (he has cited Black Flag and Electric Wizard as favorites) as well as drawing inspiration from 1960s & 1970s horror and exploitation movies.
